### Configuration (Dev)
@host = http://localhost:8080
@auth = {{host}}/api/auth
@api = {{host}}/api/modules

### ===========================================================================
### LOGIN UTILISATEURS
### ===========================================================================

### Login Admin (accès à tout)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{auth}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

### Login Pro (a acheté LIMS)
# @name loginPro
POST {{auth}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "pro@example.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

### Login Student (a acheté Inventaire)
# @name loginStudent
POST {{auth}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student@example.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

### Login Guest (aucun achat)
# @name loginGuest
POST {{auth}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "guest@example.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

### ===========================================================================
### TEST ACCÈS ADMIN (tout accessible)
### ===========================================================================

### Admin - Modules gratuits (MUNIN_ATLAS)
GET {{api}}/type/MUNIN_ATLAS
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.accessToken}}

### Admin - Modules payants (HUGIN_LAB)
GET {{api}}/type/HUGIN_LAB
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.accessToken}}

### Admin - LIMS (payant)
GET {{api}}/HUGIN_LIMS
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.accessToken}}

### ===========================================================================
### TEST ACCÈS PRO (LIMS acheté)
### ===========================================================================

### Pro - Module gratuit (OK)
GET {{api}}/MUNIN_BACTERIO
Authorization: Bearer {{loginPro.response.body.accessToken}}

### Pro - LIMS (acheté - OK)
GET {{api}}/HUGIN_LIMS
Authorization: Bearer {{loginPro.response.body.accessToken}}

### Pro - Inventaire (pas acheté - locked?)
GET {{api}}/HUGIN_INVENTORY
Authorization: Bearer {{loginPro.response.body.accessToken}}

### ===========================================================================
### TEST ACCÈS STUDENT (Inventaire acheté)
### ===========================================================================

### Student - Module gratuit (OK)
GET {{api}}/MUNIN_MYCO
Authorization: Bearer {{loginStudent.response.body.accessToken}}

### Student - Inventaire (acheté - OK)
GET {{api}}/HUGIN_INVENTORY
Authorization: Bearer {{loginStudent.response.body.accessToken}}

### Student - LIMS (pas acheté - locked?)
GET {{api}}/HUGIN_LIMS
Authorization: Bearer {{loginStudent.response.body.accessToken}}

### ===========================================================================
### TEST ACCÈS GUEST (aucun achat)
### ===========================================================================

### Guest - Module gratuit (OK)
GET {{api}}/MUNIN_VIRO
Authorization: Bearer {{loginGuest.response.body.accessToken}}

### Guest - LIMS (pas acheté - locked?)
GET {{api}}/HUGIN_LIMS
Authorization: Bearer {{loginGuest.response.body.accessToken}}

### Guest - Inventaire (pas acheté - locked?)
GET {{api}}/HUGIN_INVENTORY
Authorization: Bearer {{loginGuest.response.body.accessToken}}

### ===========================================================================
### TEST REFRESH TOKEN
### ===========================================================================

### Refresh token Admin
POST {{auth}}/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{loginAdmin.response.body.refreshToken}}"
}

### Refresh token Pro
POST {{auth}}/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{loginPro.response.body.refreshToken}}"
}

### ===========================================================================
### TEST SANS AUTH (401)
### ===========================================================================

### Sans token - doit retourner 401
GET {{api}}/MUNIN_BACTERIO

### Token invalide - doit retourner 401
GET {{api}}/MUNIN_BACTERIO
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here
